ba53a2be12f678d060c08b393abe4033669","tid":2402725,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5f4830666da91bacf54a607c33c8c950b10837","tid":2402725,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85043d7cd29bc7194c5b0b839c7a75bc470c01e","tid":2402725,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"其實10日定3個月喺阻嚇性層面係咪有咁多分別啊? <br />\n唔通「只係」坐10日啲人就會繼續都棍出街 判夠3個月就人人守法忍讓個政府咩 <br />\n現實係判得監10日定3個月阻嚇性都無分別 但對個被告自身嚟講就差天共地 希望到時你地三個喺入邊終老就會清楚個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9f3faf5085f47dc7fc95a7fd8b0b1f64c22510","tid":2402725,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaad632017632799cfee7a6d653f11fdc19312d","tid":2402725,"uid":35712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"高上情操 高上情操<br />\n車斷腳有錢收有錢收<br />\n屌你老母 721仲未有人判罪"},{"pid":"6e897921f6afd5a015f9dabcc6e4148829276aad","tid":2402725,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0135c0d676216583639c84d0c35924eba1b5f02","tid":2402725,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:51:18.000Z","msg":"三個狗官死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2e433a0ff848d25f0ac4139bfceca7ef3da2dc","tid":2402725,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:57:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">《恐怖的法官&mdash;&mdash;納粹時期的司法》<br />\n作者指出，認為納粹時代法學家對法律條文無比忠誠，是一個臆造的神話。納粹的法官不像實證法學認為的那麼尊重法治、崇尚規則；反過來說，他們心目中超越法律的自然正義，也不過是國家和領袖的意志而已。從國家理由出發，他們可以踐踏法律的界限；從對付敵人出發，他們可以變為虔誠的律法主義者。<br />\n<br />\n納粹國家是一個瘋狂運轉的機器，所向披靡，它需要法律的護衛者，需要這些法官作為零件和潤滑油。納粹統治者誠然會建立各種非法的制度，採取各種任性的手段， <span class=\"red\">但他們並不會刻意繞開法律的裝潢，專制者、極權者、暴君、惡魔其實比誰都更需要那種貌似公正的法庭，需要法律人和他們之間的莊嚴合謀及認真表演</span>。</span><br />\n唔好再話香港法治仲有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}